Installation:

    1) install vim
    2) delete _vimrc
    3) clone online repo using
    git clone ...    

Create symlinks in cmd:
    
    cd "c:Program Files (x86)\Vim"
    mklink /H ~Vim\_vimrc vimfiles\_vimrc    

Switch to the vimfiles directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd vimfiles
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

